sentence: what states border states that the mississippi runs through ?
sentence-with-vars: what states border states that the river0 runs through ?
sql: select border_info.border from border_info where border_info.state_name in ( select river.traverse from river where river.river_name = ' mississippi ' ) ;
sql-with-vars: select border_info.border from border_info where border_info.state_name in ( select river.traverse from river where river.river_name = ' river0 ' ) ;
